import asyncio

async def fetch_data(url):
    await asyncio.sleep(1)
    return f"Data from {url}"

async def main():
    tasks = [fetch_data(f"https://api.example.com/{i}") for i in range(5)]
    results = await asyncio.gather(*tasks)
    print(results)

if __name__ == "__main__":
    asyncio.run(main())
